McKinnon returns to reality and takes off Detective Hamon’s headpiece. Hamon takes a few seconds to reorient himself before getting to his feet.
<<show_character Backend 1 Hamon>>
Hamon: “You understand now?”
<<show_character Backend 0 McKinnon>>
McKinnon: “I still don’t understand why. What did Matthias mean?”
<<show_character Backend 1 Hamon>>
Hamon: “I can’t say directly, but in my twenty years, I’ve gotten to know a lot of people, McKinnon. I became friends with many of them, and in the Outer Districts, gangs are a way of life.”
<<show_character Backend 0 McKinnon>>
McKinnon: “You’re helping gangs?”
<<show_character Backend 1 Hamon>>
Hamon: “Gangs aren’t the enemy, McKinnon. You’re new around here so you don’t understand the way the OD works. It’s a way of life here. They control an area and keep order there." 
Hamon: "Conflicts are from incursions. You keep the peace between them, you keep the peace in the quadrants. You’ll understand later.”
<<show_character Backend 0 McKinnon>>
McKinnon: “If you say so. This doesn’t explain why they wanted to distribute these things anyway. The military is involved as well. It can’t be just to create more addicts, right?”
<<show_character Backend 1 Hamon>>
He shrugs.
Hamon: “I can’t say, but you know who might know?”
<<show_character Backend 0 McKinnon>>
McKinnon: “The scientist? Can you talk about him?”
<<show_character Backend 1 Hamon>>
Hamon: “Even better. Get ready. I’ll be right back, but you’re going to have to be quick.”
<<show_character Backend 0 McKinnon>>
McKinnon: “I’m sorry?”
<<show_character Backend 1 Hamon>>
Hamon: “I’m visiting a friend.”
<<fade_in Backgrounds 1>>
With that he rushes out of the room. McKinnon follows him a bit until Hamon leaves the building and decides to follow Hamon’s advice. He resets one of the stations and sets it on standby for the next use.
True to his word, Hamon returns in ten minutes with an unconscious man slung over his shoulder. Hamon places the man on a seat and McKinnon connects him to the machine. As McKinnon gets ready, Hamon goes over to the seat where Vera was sleeping.
<<fade_out Backgrounds 1>>
